definition:
question_for(goal: 'Dict[str, Any]') -> 'str'
The concrete question this goal must answer. Prefers the stored question;
    otherwise derives one from the title/subject.

recovery_probe(capability: 'str') -> 'Optional[bool]'
Run the capability's recovery probe. True/False = verified working/broken;
    None = no probe exists, so recovery cannot be verified at all.
